\[
E = \int dE_z = \frac{q}{4\pi\varepsilon_0 a^2} \int_0^{\pi/2} \sin\theta \cos\theta \, d\theta
\]

Evaluating the integral:

\[
E = \frac{q}{8\pi\varepsilon_0 a^2}
\]

